
High-level Scope:
Data collection and secure integration with NetSuite (logs, metadata, scripts, integrations, bundles)

SuiteScript performance analysis (execution time, governance usage, inefficiencies)

UI and forms performance assessment (load time, field usage, form complexity)

Customization and over-customization analysis (custom objects, workflows, redundancy, unused assets)

Integration performance assessment (API latency, failures, throughput, bottlenecks)

Bundles and installed apps analysis (usage, conflicts, performance impact)

System health scoring and benchmarking (overall score, module-wise insights, industry comparison)

AI-driven insights and recommendations (optimization suggestions, prioritization, predictive risks)

Reporting and dashboards (role-based views, drill-down insights, exportable reports)

Alerts and proactive monitoring (failures, performance degradation, threshold-based triggers)

Security and compliance checks (roles, permissions, access anomalies)

Extensibility and ecosystem support (middleware, third-party integrations, APIs)

Deployment model (SaaS vs one-time audit, continuous monitoring, multi-account support)
